item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m hans durk (han5 durk). I am a student and dreamer. Being a student, I ask questions and seek for digestible answers. Generally, it is followed by me trying to contradict my brain with wrong answers. And a dreamer, because that’s where freedom is. I generally divide my time between schoolwork, coding and making YouTube videos. Right now I’m enrolled in a Dual Degree course (B.Tech + M.Tech) in Mechanical Engineering at IIT Kharagpur as Shubham Hansda(not han5 durk).
